					<msContents class="#STM">
						<summary><p>An incomplete <title xml:lang="ta"
									>Nikaṇṭu</title>, apparently a portion of the <title
									xml:lang="ta"
									>Tivākaram</title>. The manuscript contains only the 4th part named <title
									xml:lang="ta"
								>Marappeyart Tokuti</title> ("section on the names of trees"), in 67 stanzas.</p>
							<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (September 2021).</p>
							<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>
						</summary>

